Package: AirlineReviewAnalyzer
Title: Analyze Airline Reviews for Insights
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ahmed", "Azmy Elsayed", , "azmy@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools to analyze airline reviews, perform sentiment analysis, 
    extract keywords, and visualize trends in customer feedback. It is designed to help airlines
    and analysts gain actionable insights from passenger reviews.
